2. ğŸ’¬ Inline Comment Standards

âœ… Format
// Check if plugin is enabled before proceeding.
if (!get_option('plugin_enabled')) {
    return;
}

âœ… Rules
- Use full sentences with punctuation.
- Place above logic blocks, not trailing.
- Use comments to explain:
  - Hook context:        // Fired during 'init'
  - WP behavior:         // Filters post title
  - Architecture:        // Avoids duplicate slug registration
  - Edge cases:          // Skip if post is autosave

